{"tid":1408593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"車cam直擊！克警紅燈過馬路險捱車撞 揮棍指嚇司機","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:48:24.000Z","uid":156878,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce9a442c406d7d343f28b484cb75bee5e4e850e","tid":1408593,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:43:11.000Z","msg":"昨晚（4日）黃大仙爆發警民衝突，警方出動催淚彈驅散向其喝罵的街坊，更有警員在橫過馬路時，疑未有留意交通燈號，在紅燈時走出斑馬線，險被一輛遵守交通規則的汽車撞倒。惟該警員似未察覺有關情況，反而揮棍指嚇司機，整個過程被涉事車輛的行車記錄儀拍下，並被上載至「前線警員支持大聯盟」fb專頁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190804/59895439\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190804%2F59895439&d=uztthH5CN7iuCFQPSeIHaSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=ee793184\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190804%2F59895439&h=e3e4edcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190804/59895439</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88f945a5b53e3801d251303980ca5b60b0314fa","tid":1408593,"uid":156878,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:44:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/673975979716035/videos/355744998691974/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F673975979716035%2Fvideos%2F355744998691974%2F&d=uztthH5CN7iuCFQPSeIHaSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=01cd1d47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/673975979716035/videos/355744998691974/</a>"},{"pid":"12e8e2f4fa08224fdcd6207aa0da9782d6dfdc03","tid":1408593,"uid":273234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:46:51.000Z","msg":"警棍打車?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe